        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">Tax-Efficient Investing: Complete Strategy Guide</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">Discover proven tax-efficient investing strategies, asset location rules, and ways to minimize investment taxes in your ...</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://westmountfundamentals.com/capital-gains-tax-calculator" style="display:block;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:10px;padding:1.25rem;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;transition:border-color 0.2s,transform 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,0.2)';this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,0.08)';this.style.transform='none'">
        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">Free Capital Gains Tax Calculator & Estimator (2024</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">Calculate your estimated short-term and long-term capital gains taxes with our free calculator. Understand how filing st...</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</SiteLayout>
